    SELECT u."Id", u."ActivityType", u."Description", u."Timestamp", u."UserId"
    FROM "UserActivityLogs" AS u
    WHERE u."UserId" = @__userId_0
    ORDER BY u."Timestamp" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS u1
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u0 ON u1."UserId" = u0."Id"
ORDER BY u1."Timestamp" DESC
